## Phase 5 — Blog/Insights Infrastructure

**Goal:** Build blog listing and post pages with local data.  
**Estimated complexity:** Moderate — 3 new files + 2 modified files.

### Proposed Changes

---

#### Blog Data & Pages

##### [NEW] `src/data/posts.ts`
- Typed data file exporting a `POSTS` array and helper functions: `getAllPosts()`, `getPostBySlug(slug)`, `getLatestPosts(count)`.
- Each post: `slug`, `title`, `excerpt` (2 sentences), `category` (`"Engineering"` | `"AI"` | `"Case Study"` | `"Process"`), `author`, [date](file:///f:/Techbridge/premium-next-app/src/app/websites/page.tsx#514-522) (ISO string), `readTime` (string, e.g., `"6 min read"`), `body` (multi-paragraph string content — plain text, not markdown for simplicity).
- 4 placeholder posts covering each category:
  1. "Why We Chose Next.js App Router Over Pages Router" (Engineering)
  2. "Automating Client Onboarding with AI Workflows" (AI)
  3. "How We Built NextLex in 14 Days" (Case Study)
  4. "Our 4-Phase Engineering Process, Explained" (Process)

##### [NEW] `src/app/blog/page.tsx`
- Blog listing page (Server Component).
- Section header: Eyebrow "Insights" → H2 "Engineering Thinking. → Shared Openly." (gradient on "Shared Openly").
- Card grid: 2 columns desktop, 1 mobile. Each card follows the glass card pattern:
  - Category tag pill at top.
  - Title: `text-lg font-semibold text-white`.
  - Excerpt: `text-sm text-zinc-500`, 2 lines max.
  - Footer: author name + date + read time in `text-xs text-zinc-600 font-mono`.
  - "Read →" text link CTA.
  - Whole card is a `<Link>` to `/blog/[slug]`.
- SEO: `title: "Blog | Engineering Insights — TechBridge"`, `description: "..."`.

##### [NEW] `src/app/blog/[slug]/page.tsx`
- Individual blog post page (Server Component with `generateStaticParams`).
- Clean reading layout: `max-w-3xl mx-auto`.
- Top block: category pill, title (h1), author + date + read time, back link ("← Back to Insights" text link).
- Body: rendered as paragraphs with proper spacing (`space-y-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-400`). Simple paragraph splitting on double newlines.
- Bottom: "Continue Reading" section showing 2 other posts (not the current one) as mini teaser cards.
- SEO: `generateMetadata` → `"[Post Title] | TechBridge Blog"`.

##### [MODIFY] [src/components/layout/Navbar.tsx](file:///f:/Techbridge/premium-next-app/src/components/layout/Navbar.tsx)
- Add `{ label: "Blog", href: "/blog" }` to the `NAV_LINKS` array. Insert before "About" to keep the nav flow logical: `Services | 24-Hr Studio | Work | Blog | About | Contact`.

##### [NEW] `src/components/home/LatestInsights.tsx`
- New homepage section placed after Testimonials, before CTA.
- Section header: Eyebrow "Latest Insights" → H2 "From the Engineering Team."
- Shows the 2 most recent posts as teaser cards (import `getLatestPosts(2)` from data file).
- "View All Insights →" text link CTA at box bottom, linking to `/blog`.
- Glass card pattern, stagger animation.

##### [MODIFY] [src/app/page.tsx](file:///f:/Techbridge/premium-next-app/src/app/page.tsx)
- Import `LatestInsights` and insert between `<Testimonials />` and `<CTA />`.
- Final order: `Hero → TrustedBy → Services → HowItWorks → WhyChooseUs → TechStackMarquee → CaseStudies → Testimonials → LatestInsights → CTA`.

### Work Order
1. `src/data/posts.ts` (data foundation)
2. `src/app/blog/page.tsx` (listing page)
3. `src/app/blog/[slug]/page.tsx` (detail page)
4. [Navbar.tsx](file:///f:/Techbridge/premium-next-app/src/components/layout/Navbar.tsx) (add link)
5. `LatestInsights.tsx` (homepage section)
6. [page.tsx](file:///f:/Techbridge/premium-next-app/src/app/page.tsx) (insertion)

### Decisions Needed
1. **Blog link label:** "Blog" or "Insights"? I recommend "Insights" — more premium-sounding and aligns with the section name "Latest Insights."
2. **Markdown rendering:** Should post bodies support basic markdown (bold, links, code blocks), or is plain paragraph text sufficient for now? I recommend **plain text for now** to keep the scope tight — markdown support can be added later.

